docs.lead_paragraph: An invitation to Americans with money and real appreciation of old houses and estates to so to England and either rent or buy those which are constantly going on the market has been issued by the Rev. Dr. Dugald Macfadyen of Letchworth, England, who has come to this country as a member of the British and American Interchange Commission and will remain until August.
